<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/nov/19/">&#x27a0;</a> November 19, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="ev1servers_rapidssl" >

        
        <a name="002123"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.ev1servers.net/hosting/ssl/starterssl_details.asp">EV1Servers - RapidSSL</a></h4>

        

        <p>This isn&#8217;t a bad deal at all:  $15 for an SSL certificate recognized as valid by any moderately-recent webbrowser.  Perfect for your home-run webmail server.</p>

