    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Linux on TV</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2500245/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Linux on TV" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/1/2500245_fa90b9d0df_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>I finally got around to hacking my Linux laptop to enable the SVideo out.  Hurrah!  Now I can watch <a href="http://www.uknova.com/">UKNova</a> downloads on TV!  (The screenshot you see is <a href="http://www.mythtv.org/">MythTV</a> compiling)</p>
        </p>

